{"tid":2116490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： Notepad++新版本「Stand with HK」 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-07-20T07:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T09:14:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34ad51738412c80f2f64c79a256e6e35e8f58f2d","tid":2116490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200720/V2V6CUPIPTRFA3BSRT7ELOCLWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200720%2FV2V6CUPIPTRFA3BSRT7ELOCLWY%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=d866413c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200720%2FV2V6CUPIPTRFA3BSRT7ELOCLWY%2F&h=ae988c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200720/V2V6CUPIPTRFA3BSRT7ELOCLWY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\nNotepad++新版本「Stand with HK」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LgYtDwaqzzUscCTh3Sv_XXpoOac=/757x519/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YRQQKEHSLOHDPRMFE4HY4WIVLA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLgYtDwaqzzUscCTh3Sv_XXpoOac%3D%2F757x519%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYRQQKEHSLOHDPRMFE4HY4WIVLA.gif&h=128dcdb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNotepad++改咗新版本個名公開撐港，應該好快俾大陸禁用。<br />\n<br />\n自從美國總統特朗普簽咗《香港自治法》同取消香港特殊地位嘅行政命令，國際社會對香港關注似乎靜咗，但咁唔代表忘記咗香港，好似Windows平台文字編輯軟件 Notepad++咁吖，為咗聲援香港人，上星期推出嘅新版本，就用「Stand with Hong Kong」命名。<br />\n<br />\nNotepad++嘅開發者Don Ho仲撰文，提到去年 6 月至今，數以百萬計港人為咗自由同自治抗爭，。。。。。。。。。。。。。八方估計Notepad++好快會俾大陸禁用。"},{"pid":"e5439604171ebaee9cce73b7d7d9f78fe20ab94b","tid":2116490,"uid":270943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a8f4a0c0ca5b80c9d8216c76a38b4f88b68fa6","tid":2116490,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870e1f048d12f483d0d02431596b20a6421f507b","tid":2116490,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"呢個有得玩下"}]}